edu.xtec.util

Class Check

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.util.Check

  • public class Check
extends Object
    This class is useful to display a warning message when a specific requirement is not satisfied. Examples of unsatisfied requirements are the ability to instantiate a specific class, to access to a file or resource, or to have specific permissions. The message can be stored into an HTML resource, and will be displayed in a JEditorPane. Users will be able to follow the links included in the HTML document.
    Version:
    13.08.29
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
